        <name xml:lang="en">Phosphate</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Estimation. The sodium phosphate from the phosphoric acid neutralization is assumed to leave the production process with the wastewater. Further it is assumed that this wastewater is treated in a internal wastewater plant. The removal efficiency for phosphate is assumed with 51.8%. The removed phosphate is accounted as inert waste.</comment>
